# Building Zashi for the iOS Simulator

## Booted Simulator

**iPhone 16 Pro** — device ID: `E0BBD5AF-CC50-4A55-BC6A-1DEDF7646AEB`

If it's Shutdown, boot it first:
```bash
xcrun simctl boot E0BBD5AF-CC50-4A55-BC6A-1DEDF7646AEB && open -a Simulator
```

## Build Command

Always set `FX_ENABLE_GLASS=0` — Flexa 1.1.4 enables iOS 26 glass UI by default, which fails to compile on Xcode 16.

```bash
cd /Users/roman/projects/zally/zashi-ios && FX_ENABLE_GLASS=0 xcodebuild \
  -scheme secant-mainnet \
  -destination 'id=E0BBD5AF-CC50-4A55-BC6A-1DEDF7646AEB' \
  -configuration Debug \
  build 2>&1
```

Build takes ~2min (incremental) after the first full build.

## Install & Launch

Bundle ID: `co.valargroup.secant-mainnet`

```bash
xcrun simctl install E0BBD5AF-CC50-4A55-BC6A-1DEDF7646AEB \
  "/Users/roman/Library/Developer/Xcode/DerivedData/secant-cxtkthuvtjsyjbggllztalvjlqmb/Build/Products/Debug-iphonesimulator/secant-mainnet.app"

xcrun simctl launch E0BBD5AF-CC50-4A55-BC6A-1DEDF7646AEB co.valargroup.secant-mainnet
```

## Terminate & Relaunch

```bash
xcrun simctl terminate E0BBD5AF-CC50-4A55-BC6A-1DEDF7646AEB co.valargroup.secant-mainnet
xcrun simctl launch E0BBD5AF-CC50-4A55-BC6A-1DEDF7646AEB co.valargroup.secant-mainnet
```

## Notes

- `secant-mainnet` with `-configuration Debug` uses **mainnet** lightwalletd (`zec.rocks:443`). The scheme sets `SECANT_MAINNET` in `SWIFT_ACTIVE_COMPILATION_CONDITIONS`, and `TargetConstants.zcashNetwork` checks `#if SECANT_MAINNET` (not `#if DEBUG`). Do NOT use `-configuration Release` — the Debug build is correct and much faster.
- The voting backend is controlled by `secant/Resources/voting-config-local.json` (bundled override, takes priority over CDN in Debug builds). Keep this pointed at `https://46-101-255-48.sslip.io` for remote testing, or `http://localhost:1318` for local chain.
- If xcodebuild hangs at "Resolve Package Graph" for >2min, kill it (`pkill -f xcodebuild`) and retry — a previous build process likely left a lock.
